metadata.name: EVE.exe/ TETANDID
metadata.description:
AI+PHOTOSHOP+ILLUSTRATOR  
Eve.exe, the first robot to set foot on the planet, stands as a marvel of technological innovation and human ingenuity. As Eve.exe explores the uncharted landscapes of this distant world, she carries the hopes and dreams of humanity, paving the way for future advancements and discoveries in the realm of robotics and space exploration.
